{
    "analysis": "From the previous aggregates we have global thresholds (P95) per component-KPI: memory (mem) P95 is especially high for catalogue-db, orders, shipping, queue-master, front-end, and there are notable diskio P95 values for carts-db and user-db. Logs show no error_count spikes; front-end and queue-master have high log.row_count. No trace aggregates were returned. To proceed following the prescribed workflow, we must now perform anomaly detection inside the incident window using the precomputed global thresholds (P95) for each component-KPI. This will tell us which component-KPIs actually breached their global thresholds during 2024-01-20 01:21:01 to 2024-01-20 01:51:01 UTC and provide earliest anomaly times and severity to prioritize root-cause candidates.",
